# CloudFront security & edge functions

## Security knobs

- **ACM cert** for a custom domain — **must be in `us-east-1`** (classic gotcha)
- **Viewer** vs **origin protocol policy** — independent; encrypt ≥ the viewer leg
- **Geo restriction** — allow/blocklist by country (403), before cache
- **Signed URLs / cookies** — time-bounded private content

## Edge functions

- **CloudFront Functions** — JS, **viewer only**, **sub-1 ms**, no network, ~6× cheaper, **millions/sec** → URL rewrites, cache-key normalization, headers
- **Lambda@Edge** — Node/Python, **all 4 triggers**, 5–30 s, **network access**, thousands/sec → auth calls, origin rewrites

**Rule:** Functions for cheap viewer-edge work; Lambda@Edge when it needs the network / origin side.
